2:40.000Z","msg":"果欄，黑社會+廢老混合體"},{"pid":"caa66099da4789247830ad2812a1e3af26715d7e","tid":1822513,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c4acd051adab1fc5bea926bc027d7bbeea2da4","tid":1822513,"uid":34352,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"都on9<br />\n花墟不知幾撚多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同上2年都冇分別，又係到唱淡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:13:13.000Z","msg":"真?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6344ed217dffdd8e0a4196c3b550089bfd5c6ba4","tid":1822513,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61c5369ccb61eee9e9effdbf19e267a198207bc1","tid":1822513,"uid":38651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f86370cd900270f3cbcd43171eccc4fae61594de","tid":1822513,"uid":86675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:27:54.000Z","msg":"條街同商場好旺喎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:01:43.000Z","msg":"我都覺 感覺上真係多番人<br />\n賣新年利是裝飾個啲鋪頭都好多人睇<br />\n唔敢話生意點 但都起碼有人流"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:13:44.000Z","msg":"旺丁不旺財無意思<br />\n就算生意多返少少，都好難上返6月前既水平<br />\n更重要係租金，仲係幾個月前咁，幾多個業主肯陪你捱減租？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2f17277785806adf75646dccff06a220983e1e","tid":1822513,"uid":246329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:13:48.000Z","msg":"根本就全部都係劏遊客同大陸人既生意尼 <br />\n咁政府攪左咁樣一壇大獲野 好難唔受影響既 <br />\n不過反正佢地又唔敢鬧政府 彩佢都傻既 由佢自生自滅咪得<br />\n<br />\n做本地人生意既邊間受到影響? 有既 受影響變好左lo <br />\n睇下燉就知生意幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />市道邊有變差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />官媒實證生意爆棚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adbcab6d74c8d39ef8fe76fc8d0ab2bcaec60b6","tid":1822513,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:14:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hk